{"tid":87650,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[欖球撚召喚]有冇人有睇All Out？","createTime":"2017-01-20T04:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T09:38:07.000Z","uid":6776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b118f907b94500c951ecb22cc4ecd23aba1b2ab5","tid":87650,"uid":6776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:05:14.000Z","msg":"新果集動畫好正 <br />\n江文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e704eb59609089843dbc9bf1569695c9e1b829a","tid":87650,"uid":20943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:11:51.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗江交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過其實橄欖球同美式足球有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲興趣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d46b69010e514cab479d29e326d3641a27db3e","tid":87650,"uid":6776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯咗江交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過其實橄欖球同美式足球有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲興趣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美足係欖球演變出嚟<br />\n兩者正常都只可以向後傳，欖球用腳就可以向前<br />\n而美足有一次向前傳嘅機會，而且佢打法係用攻勢去爭取碼數，冇記錯係每一波最少要向前十碼，先可以繼續，直至達陣，如果唔係就要change over。<br />\n達陣都有少少分別，美足係你到左達陣區已經搞掂，而欖球你要個波掂地先計入波，所以即使到左try zone比人撞出底綫／向前跌波，一樣唔計入<br />\n另一個最大分別係，美足要帶甲打"},{"pid":"7daa8196ee2fb4be61ef375b7e78a8179e39833f","tid":87650,"uid":7212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯咗江交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過其實橄欖球同美式足球有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲興趣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美足係欖球演變出嚟<br />\n兩者正常都只可以向後傳，欖球用腳就可以向前<br />\n而美足有一次向前傳嘅機會，而且佢打法係用攻勢去爭取碼數，冇記錯係每一波最少要向前十碼，先可以繼續，直至達陣，如果唔係就要change over。<br />\n達陣都有少少分別，美足係你到左達陣區已經搞掂，而欖球你要個波掂地先計入波，所以即使到左try zone比人撞出底綫／向前跌波，一樣唔計入<br />\n另一個最大分別係，美足要帶甲打</blockquote><br />\n另外，人數都會有好大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普遍黎講<br />\nRugby 有 7人制（流行）、10人制、15人制（傳統）<br />\nAmerican football 就 11打11，但一隊美式足球隊嘅人數係可以去到30幾人以上，因為佢係分offensive team （11）、Defensive Team (11)同special team (11)，未計後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db864d835151dd95c373c9e66f0ca748f81edcd9","tid":87650,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"巴打係有睇開？<br />\n有冇選手可以乜鳩都唔理，攬住個球一路撞開人一路衝去達陣？"},{"pid":"fd3580f40c8ef893a6caee0f348c58385cd34881","tid":87650,"uid":26618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得江文跑得又識接波，表情同造型似蛭魔？<br />\nbtw，all out有無可能去到eyeshield咁紅？"},{"pid":"46c3e84cef277913a92dd79c4f1281b320be5788","tid":87650,"uid":26618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"第九集對相模，隊長流血後，全隊表現超熱血。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e534c73e5599f454a232de2e72d50e54c77ab1b","tid":87650,"uid":6776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係有睇開？<br />\n有冇選手可以乜鳩都唔理，攬住個球一路撞開人一路衝去達陣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上冇<br />\n不過的確係有啲怪物級球員係要幾條友先停到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全盛嘅Jonah Lomu就係其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef223c0d0a8aac9fe2c8c819f6da78c3dbc7c19","tid":87650,"uid":6776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:48:29.000Z","m